    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Requirements</strong> You just used the @UUID[Compendium.pf2e-adventures-in-etheirys.actions.Item.zJ3Jakto3oqJTLZR]{Limit Break} action.</p><hr /><p>You wreathe your weapon in elemental energy, briefly turning it into a weapon of pure elemental power. When you learn this Limit Break, choose fire, ice, lightning, water, or wind. This Limit Break gains the corresponding elemental trait. When you use this Limit Break, make a melee or ranged Strike. If the Strike hits, you deal damage of your chosen elemental type rather than the normal damage type of the weapon, as well as an additional 1d6 points of elemental damage per weapon die.</p><p>Damage dealt by Spinning Edge ignores resistance to the element, and downgrades immunity to resistance equal to the target's level.</p>",
